            <p><strong><a href="http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/2016/10/14/dot-bans-samsung-galaxy-note-7-flights/92066322/" target="_blank">FAA Bans Samsung Galaxy Note 7 From Flights After Smartphones Recalled, Discontinued</a></strong></p>
            <p>After nearly 100 reports of Galaxy Note 7 smartphones overheating, and in some cases injuring users or damaging property, the FAA has banned the devices from all airlines. This announcement represents only the latest blow to Samsung, which has already issued two recalls of this product and ultimately discontinued it.</p>
