            <p><strong><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/19/arts/design/watch-gifs-bring-history-to-life-patriotic-squirrel-included.html" target="_blank">The Federal Government’s Latest Project: Squirrel GIFs</a></strong></p>
